The book on spatz been written already.<br>
Its easy to read, every home has it, but the problem is that most people can't figure out if they should read it from the top or the bottom. So they sit there and stare at it and then rip off a dozen or so sheets, use them, flush the toilet and leave the rest of the reading until next time. 
